Package: r.assistant
Title: AI-Powered Programming Assistant for R
Version: 0.6.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Gavin", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "gavin@example.com")
Description: An AI-powered coding assistant for R and RStudio, similar to 
    Posit Assistant. Supports code generation, explanation, refactoring, 
    error diagnosis, and documentation via configurable LLM APIs (OpenAI, 
    Anthropic, DeepSeek, and any OpenAI-compatible endpoint). Includes 
    RStudio addins for interactive chat, inline code completion, and 
    context-aware assistance.
